name: RTCIceCandidatePairStats.localCandidateId
description: The RTCIceCandidatePairStats property localCandidateId is a string that uniquely identifies the local ICE candidate which was analyzed to generate the RTCIceCandidateStats used to compute the statistics for this pair of candidates.
